{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllBarComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent03BarB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of bar","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBarComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BarComponentTokens"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bar"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Bar"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProviders"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":"), borders (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and effects (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllEffectSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:borders:colors:opacities:effects:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/borders","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/colors","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/effects","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/opacities","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/sizes"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/BarComponentTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for bar component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomBarComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the bar component tokens you want.","","        override var colorBgOpaque: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.bgTertiary }","","        override var effectBgBlur: EffectSemanticToken { EffectRawTokens.blur320 }","","        override var borderRadiusActiveIndicatorCustomTop: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.radiusPill }","","        override var sizeWidthActiveIndicatorCustomBottom: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._650 }","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomBarComponentTokensProvider: BarComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"code":"CustomBBarComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(bar: CustomBarComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(bar: CustomBarComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBordersSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeEffectSemanticTokensProvider for effects","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeOpacitiySemanticTokensProvider for opacities","    let barComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own providers","    let barComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider(","                    sizes: CustomSizesSemanticTokensProvider(),","                    colors: CustomColorsSemanticTokensProvider(), ...)"]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.22.0"}]}],"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebarcomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B31ThemeBarComponentTokensProviderC","title":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"}]},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider/colors":{"title":"colors","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemes